'''[[Cannabis]] in [[Belarus]]''' is illegal.

==Cultivation==
A 1996 report noted that cultivation of cannabis was present in Belarus, fueling usage in the country; the same report noted that personal possession of cannabis was not at that time illegal.<ref name="MattersAffairs1996">{{cite book|author1=United States. Dept. of State. Bureau of International Narcotics Matters|author2=United States. Bureau for International Narcotics and Law Enforcement Affairs|title=International narcotics control strategy report|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=nNEWAAAAYAAJ|date=1 June 1996|publisher=The Bureau|isbn=978-0-16-048569-5|page=332}}</ref> Though production and use of cannabis was already illegal, on 31 December 2016 Belarus also banned the cultivation of cannabis.<ref>[https://sputniknews.com/europe/201612311049155039-belarus-bans-cannabis/ Belarus Fully Bans Cannabis, Opium Poppy Cultivation]. Sputnik International, 20161231</ref>

